                <formatted-text>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#b07aa1'>Use the toggles above to toggle the work setup type (i.e. Remote, Hybrid, Onsite). 
</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#b07aa1'>Remote has the highest average work life balance rating out of all the setups (indiscriminate of the region), with a significant difference, demonstrating that remote work arrangements provide better work life balance opportunities for employees.</run>
